---
import Site from '../layouts/Site.astro';
import '../styles/inside.css';
---
<Site
  title="Inside Navon — The people behind the platform"
  description="Leadership, advisors, and how we work. The team building sovereign deep-tech infrastructure for emerging markets."
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="mark"></span>Inside Navon</div>
      <h1 class="page-title reveal">The people behind<br/><span class="accent">the platform.</span></h1>
      <p class="page-lede reveal d1" style="margin-top:24px;">
        Operators, engineers, financiers, and educators — assembled
        across continents to build sovereign compute on the ground.
      </p>
    </div>
    <svg class="hero-glyph tech draw" viewBox="0 0 460 380" aria-hidden="true">
      <g class="hair">
        <circle cx="120" cy="120" r="32" fill="none"/>
        <circle cx="240" cy="80"  r="32" fill="none"/>
        <circle cx="360" cy="140" r="32" fill="none"/>
        <circle cx="160" cy="240" r="32" fill="none"/>
        <circle cx="290" cy="240" r="32" fill="none"/>
        <circle cx="100" cy="320" r="20" fill="none"/>
        <circle cx="380" cy="310" r="20" fill="none"/>
      </g>
      <g class="dashed">
        <line x1="148" y1="135" x2="212" y2="95"/>
        <line x1="268" y1="95"  x2="332" y2="125"/>
        <line x1="148" y1="148" x2="160" y2="210"/>
        <line x1="270" y1="115" x2="290" y2="210"/>
        <line x1="350" y1="167" x2="290" y2="215"/>
      </g>
      <circle cx="240" cy="80" r="6" class="signal"/>
      <circle cx="240" cy="80" r="10" class="signal pulse" opacity="0.4"/>
      <text x="60" y="370" font-size="10" letter-spacing="2" fill="#9E9F9B" font-family="JetBrains Mono">7 LEADERS · 8 ADVISORS · ONE BUILD</text>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Leadership -->
<section class="leadership">
  <div class="section-head" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="mark"></span>Leadership</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Operators &amp;<br/>builders, <span class="accent">on the ground.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="section-lede reveal d1">
      Decades of compounded experience across AI, quantum technology,
      data centres, energy, and growth-market finance — pulled together
      to build one stack, end-to-end.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="lead-grid">
    <article class="lead-card reveal d1">
      <div class="lead-portrait">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="tech draw" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="50" cy="38" r="14" class="hair" fill="none"/>
          <path class="hair" d="M22 80 C 28 65, 40 58, 50 58 C 60 58, 72 65, 78 80" fill="none"/>
          <line x1="20" y1="80" x2="80" y2="80" class="thin"/>
        </svg>
        <img src="assets/team/romi.jpg" alt="Romi Sumaria" onerror="this.remove()">
      </div>
      <div class="role">CEO &amp; Co-Founder</div>
      <h3>Romi Sumaria</h3>
      <p>Entrepreneur and investor. Director of business development in deep tech, with operating roots across growth markets.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="lead-card reveal d2">
      <div class="lead-portrait">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="tech draw" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="50" cy="38" r="14" class="hair" fill="none"/>
          <path class="hair" d="M22 80 C 28 65, 40 58, 50 58 C 60 58, 72 65, 78 80" fill="none"/>
          <rect x="42" y="35" width="16" height="6" class="signal" opacity="0.6"/>
          <line x1="20" y1="80" x2="80" y2="80" class="thin"/>
        </svg>
        <img src="assets/team/karan.jpg" alt="Karan Pinto" onerror="this.remove()">
      </div>
      <div class="role">CTO &amp; Co-Founder</div>
      <h3>Karan Pinto</h3>
      <p>Entrepreneur, board advisor, AI &amp; quantum specialist. Director of growth and infrastructure architecture.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="lead-card reveal d3">
      <div class="lead-portrait">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="tech draw" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="50" cy="38" r="14" class="hair" fill="none"/>
          <path class="hair" d="M22 80 C 28 65, 40 58, 50 58 C 60 58, 72 65, 78 80" fill="none"/>
          <line x1="20" y1="80" x2="80" y2="80" class="thin"/>
        </svg>
        <img src="assets/team/erin.jpg" alt="Erin Beilharz" onerror="this.remove()">
      </div>
      <div class="role">Founding Team &amp; Senior Advisor</div>
      <h3>Erin Beilharz</h3>
      <p>AI governance, ESG for IT and innovation, MD partnerships, cleantech hub leadership.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="lead-card reveal d1">
      <div class="lead-portrait">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="tech draw" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="50" cy="38" r="14" class="hair" fill="none"/>
          <path class="hair" d="M22 80 C 28 65, 40 58, 50 58 C 60 58, 72 65, 78 80" fill="none"/>
          <line x1="20" y1="80" x2="80" y2="80" class="thin"/>
        </svg>
        <img src="assets/team/ankush.jpg" alt="Ankush Shah" onerror="this.remove()">
      </div>
      <div class="role">CFO</div>
      <h3>Ankush Shah</h3>
      <p>Cross-border finance and investment leadership. Managing Director at Sumaria Group, Partner at Rank Ventures.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="lead-card reveal d2">
      <div class="lead-portrait">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="tech draw" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="50" cy="38" r="14" class="hair" fill="none"/>
          <path class="hair" d="M22 80 C 28 65, 40 58, 50 58 C 60 58, 72 65, 78 80" fill="none"/>
          <line x1="20" y1="80" x2="80" y2="80" class="thin"/>
        </svg>
        <img src="assets/team/ben.jpg" alt="Ben Roberts" onerror="this.remove()">
      </div>
      <div class="role">Head of Africa</div>
      <h3>Ben Roberts</h3>
      <p>Former CTO and Senior Advisor across optical networks. Decades of African telecom and infrastructure leadership.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="lead-card reveal d3">
      <div class="lead-portrait">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="tech draw" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="50" cy="38" r="14" class="hair" fill="none"/>
          <path class="hair" d="M22 80 C 28 65, 40 58, 50 58 C 60 58, 72 65, 78 80" fill="none"/>
          <line x1="20" y1="80" x2="80" y2="80" class="thin"/>
        </svg>
        <img src="assets/team/muhoro.jpg" alt="Muhoro Gathecha" onerror="this.remove()">
      </div>
      <div class="role">Head of Business Development</div>
      <h3>Muhoro Gathecha</h3>
      <p>East Africa, Sokoflow and Frontier Partner. Operating leadership across regional infrastructure.</p>
    </article>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- Advisors marquee -->
<section class="advisors">
  <div class="label mono">Advisors ↓</div>
  <div class="ad-marquee" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/karl.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>KH</span>'"></span><span class="name">Karl Harvard</span><span class="role">Nscale · ex-AWS EMEA</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/ingvil.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>IS</span>'"></span><span class="name">Ingvil Smines Tybring-Gjedde</span><span class="role">Founder · Kyros Cloud</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/urav.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>US</span>'"></span><span class="name">Urav Shah</span><span class="role">Founding Team · Entrepreneur</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/mitun.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>MP</span>'"></span><span class="name">Mitun Patel</span><span class="role">Energy · Central Africa</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/steve.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>SS</span>'"></span><span class="name">Steve Suarez</span><span class="role">CEO · Horizon X · ex-HSBC</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/maryann.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>ML</span>'"></span><span class="name">Maryann Løcka</span><span class="role">Founder · Kyros Cloud</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/samir.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>SS</span>'"></span><span class="name">Samir Shah</span><span class="role">ex-CEO · Sil Africa</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/robert.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>RK</span>'"></span><span class="name">Robert Kruschbersky</span><span class="role">Hitachi Private Equity</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/jim.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>JR</span>'"></span><span class="name">Jim Rowland</span><span class="role">Delta Electronics · DC Infrastructure</span></span>
    <!-- duplicated for seamless scroll -->
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/karl.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>KH</span>'"></span><span class="name">Karl Harvard</span><span class="role">Nscale · ex-AWS EMEA</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/ingvil.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>IS</span>'"></span><span class="name">Ingvil Smines Tybring-Gjedde</span><span class="role">Founder · Kyros Cloud</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/urav.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>US</span>'"></span><span class="name">Urav Shah</span><span class="role">Founding Team · Entrepreneur</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/mitun.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>MP</span>'"></span><span class="name">Mitun Patel</span><span class="role">Energy · Central Africa</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/steve.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>SS</span>'"></span><span class="name">Steve Suarez</span><span class="role">CEO · Horizon X · ex-HSBC</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/maryann.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>ML</span>'"></span><span class="name">Maryann Løcka</span><span class="role">Founder · Kyros Cloud</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/samir.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>SS</span>'"></span><span class="name">Samir Shah</span><span class="role">ex-CEO · Sil Africa</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/robert.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>RK</span>'"></span><span class="name">Robert Kruschbersky</span><span class="role">Hitachi Private Equity</span></span>
    <span class="ad-card"><span class="ad-portrait"><img src="assets/team/jim.jpg" alt="" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<span class=&quot;placeholder&quot;>JR</span>'"></span><span class="name">Jim Rowland</span><span class="role">Delta Electronics · DC Infrastructure</span></span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How we work -->
<section class="work">
  <div class="section-head" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="mark"></span>How we work</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Three tenets,<br/>tested <span class="accent">on every site.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="section-lede reveal d1">
      The operating principles behind how we hire, deploy, and partner.
      They've been hard-won — from running networks across the continent
      and shipping infrastructure into places everyone else said couldn't take it.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="numbered cols-3 reveal">
    <div class="numbered-item">
      <div class="num">01 / PRESENCE</div>
      <h4>We build where the work is.</h4>
      <p>On-the-ground operators in every region we serve. Engineers who know which substation matters. No air-freighted spares from Frankfurt forever.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="numbered-item">
      <div class="num">02 / INTEGRATION</div>
      <h4>Vertical stack, horizontal partners.</h4>
      <p>The stack is ours, end-to-end. The relationships around it — equipment, capital, universities, governments — are earned and reciprocal.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="numbered-item">
      <div class="num">03 / CAPACITY</div>
      <h4>We hire for the next site.</h4>
      <p>Always slightly ahead of demand, never behind. Onboarding compounds; the second site is faster than the first because the second hire was already in seat.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How we hire -->
<section class="hire">
  <div class="hire-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="mark"></span>How we hire</div>
      <h2 class="reveal">If you can build it,<br/><span class="accent">we want to talk.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal d1">
      <p style="color:var(--light); font-size:16.5px; line-height:1.6; max-width:46ch; margin:0 0 20px;">
        We're hiring across infrastructure engineering, cloud operations, cybersecurity, business development, and field engineering. Most roles are based at Hells Gate (Naivasha), Nairobi, or remote with travel.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--mid); font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; max-width:46ch; margin:0 0 24px;">
        Internships at Hells Gate run year-round for university partners. Email <a href="mailto:careers@navonworld.com" style="color: var(--signal); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(231,255,0,0.4);">careers@navonworld.com</a> with a one-page brief and we'll respond within five working days.
      </p>
      <div class="roles">
        <a class="role-pill" href="mailto:careers@navonworld.com">Infrastructure engineering →</a>
        <a class="role-pill" href="mailto:careers@navonworld.com">Cloud operations →</a>
        <a class="role-pill" href="mailto:careers@navonworld.com">Cybersecurity →</a>
        <a class="role-pill" href="mailto:careers@navonworld.com">Business development →</a>
        <a class="role-pill" href="mailto:careers@navonworld.com">Site engineering →</a>
        <a class="role-pill" href="mailto:careers@navonworld.com">Internships →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Site>
